853
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:15,120
Grand opening special: 20% off.

854
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,080
Please come in.

855
00:41:18,720 --> 00:41:20,160
Please, this way.

856
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,680
Come this way, please.

857
00:41:40,680 --> 00:41:41,600
When you go home,

858
00:41:41,600 --> 00:41:42,920
have your wife

859
00:41:43,200 --> 00:41:44,640
massage you in the morning.

860
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:46,370
Let me teach you two movements.

861
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,040
Look,

862
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:48,640
stretch your leg backward

863
00:41:49,160 --> 00:41:50,280
and extend it fully.

864
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,440
See this heel?

865
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,320
Hold for five seconds,

866
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:55,200
then switch to the other side. Remember that.

867
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:58,080
And this movement goes with body technique.

868
00:41:58,720 --> 00:42:00,440
Tilt your neck upward.

869
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,360
Upward.

870
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:02,680
Oh my!

871
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:09,720
Do we know each other?

872
00:42:17,680 --> 00:42:18,440
Dr. Liu.

873
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:20,500
I'll head back first then.

874
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:24,000
Wow! When did you get back?

875
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:24,800
Just got back.

876
00:42:25,720 --> 00:42:28,240
This shop hasn't changed in ten years.

877
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,160
What do you mean it hasn't changed?

878
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:31,680
I replace these banners every three months.

879
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:33,560
Your hair...

880
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,480
Is this

881
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:35,320
fashionable?

882
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,200
This color -

883
00:42:37,560 --> 00:42:38,680
would you dare to dye yours like this?

884
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:39,610
I wouldn't dare.

885
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:42,320
I heard from my father

886
00:42:42,320 --> 00:42:43,920
your business is booming.

887
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:46,800
Why didn't you take over this shop before?

888
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:48,600
You let him sell chestnuts here.

889
00:42:48,640 --> 00:42:49,920
I'm doing well just to manage

890
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:51,520
this one shop properly.

891
00:42:51,520 --> 00:42:54,000
That young Liu from the shop across the street

892
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,130
got arrested again.

893
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:56,040
Got arrested again?
